item.name: Employer_Setup

request.description: Before running the API sequence, employer is deleted from the system.  Deleting the employer because we are  using the same employer to run this collection multiple times and employerEmailId is unique. For this API sequence employer name used is Contribution_Option_Scope.

request.description:
Self-funded plans are always assigned to broker with an employer tag to identify the employer for whom these plans were created. 

This API is used to retrieve the list of eligible and assigned plans for the employer and their details, including plan name, carrier name, date and enrollment year. With this Api I am retrieving all the self-funded plans available in the broker for the year 2020.
